{"word":"G4100 - πιστεύω - pisteúō - pist-yoo'-o - Believe","slug":"G4100","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">πιστεύω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pisteúō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>pist-yoo'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Believe"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B9;&#x03C3;&#x03C4;&#x03B5;&#x03C5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - pisteuo&#x0304;</b> - <i>pist-yoo'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4102\">G4102</a>; to <i>have faith</i> (in, upon, or with respect to, a person or thing), that is, <i>credit</i>; by implication to <i>entrust</i> (especially one&rsquo;s spiritual well being to Christ): - believe (-r), commit (to trust), put in trust with."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G3640\">G3640</a>, <a href=\"#/G4102\">G4102</a>, <a href=\"#/G4103\">G4103</a>, <a href=\"#/G4104\">G4104</a>, <a href=\"#/G569\">G569</a>, <a href=\"#/G570\">G570</a>, <a href=\"#/G571\">G571</a>"}]}